    <stitle>ELECTRICAL SYSTEM TROUBLESHOOTING GUIDE - 9800 - IC BUS SERVICE MANUAL - DOORS AND ACCESSORIES -
        MAINTENANCE
    </stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="pm" graphiccount="0">
        <title>MAINTENANCE</title>
        <para>Suggested maintenance includes periodic inspection of attachment fasteners for evidence of loosening due
            to tampering and regular cleaning with mild soap and water. Although there are other cleaning solutions
            available, some of them contain solvents and other chemicals that can attack the high strength materials
            used in the production of the roof hatch.
        </para>
    </svcproc>
